<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Reply from Blue Sky Organisation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #191b1f;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #0000FF;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .label {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <table class="container">
    <tr>
      <td>
        <div class="header">Reply from Blue Sky Organisation</div>

        <div class="section">
          <p><b>Dear <%= name %>,</b></p>
          <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have received your message and appreciate your interest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <p><span class="label">Your Message:</span></p>
          <p><%= message %></p>

          <p><span class="label">Submitted on:</span> <%= contact_on %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <p><span class="label">Our Response:</span></p>
          <p><%= reply %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <p>If you have any further questions or concerns, feel free to reply to this email. We are always here to help.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <p>Best regards,<br />
            Blue Sky Team</p>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="footer">
    Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear(); %> Blue Sky Organisation. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>

</html>
